{
  "version": "0.4",
  "title": "XCP Service: Corporate Portraits & Headshots — Sub-page",
  "type": "page",
  "content": [
    {
      "id": "corp_hero",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Corporate Portraits Hero",
        "layout": "full_width",
        "background_image": {
          "url": "[uc_local]assets/images/corporate-portraits-hero.jpg"
        },
        "content_position": "middle"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "corp_hero_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 100
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "corp_eyebrow",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Corporate Portraits & Headshots</p>"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "corp_title",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Professional Portraits That Make the Right First Impression",
                "header_size": "h1",
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "corp_subtitle",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Corporate headshots and team portraits for businesses, executives, and professionals. Relaxed, directed, and calibrated to your brand's visual identity — whether that is traditional and authoritative or approachable and modern.</p>"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "corp_cta_button",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "button",
              "settings": {
                "text": "Book Corporate Portraits",
                "link": {
                  "url": "/contact",
                  "is_external": false,
                  "nofollow": false
                },
                "align": "center"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "corp_overview",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Corporate Portraits Overview",
        "layout": "boxed",
        "structure": "20"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "corp_overview_text_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 60,
            "_column_size_tablet": 100,
            "_column_size_mobile": 100
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "corp_overview_heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "From Individual Headshots to Full Team Portraits",
                "header_size": "h2"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "corp_overview_text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>The right headshot tells your story before you open your mouth. Whether you need a single director portrait for your website, or a consistent suite of portraits for a team of fifty, XCP Photography delivers portraits that are confident, consistent, and unmistakably you.</p><p>I specialise in making portrait sessions relaxed for non-camera-comfortable subjects — a critical skill that most photographers underestimate. The result is imagery that looks natural rather than forced.</p><ul><li>Individual executive and director portraits</li><li>Team portraits for websites, press releases, and LinkedIn</li><li>On-location at your offices, or in a controlled studio environment</li><li>Consistent background and lighting across all team members</li><li>Express turnaround options available for time-sensitive needs</li><li>Batch session discounts for teams of five or more</li><li>Retouching to professional publication standard</li></ul>"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "corp_overview_image_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 40,
            "_column_size_tablet": 100,
            "_column_size_mobile": 100
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "corp_overview_image",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "image",
              "settings": {
                "image": {
                  "url": "[uc_local]assets/images/corporate-portraits-overview.jpg"
                },
                "image_size": "large"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "corp_closing_cta",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Corporate Portraits Closing CTA",
        "layout": "boxed"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "corp_closing_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 100,
            "text_align": "center"
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "corp_closing_heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Your Team Deserves to Look the Part",
                "header_size": "h2",
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "corp_closing_text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Tell me how many people you need, where you are based, and your preferred timeline. I will respond within 24 hours with a clear proposal and transparent pricing.</p>"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "corp_closing_button",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "button",
              "settings": {
                "text": "Get a Portrait Quote",
                "link": {
                  "url": "/contact",
                  "is_external": false,
                  "nofollow": false
                },
                "align": "center"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
